            h1 aWearable Toolkit
            <br>
            <div id="about">
            <p> The aWearable toolkit is a toolkit for creating wearable location- aware applications.<br> It is made up of two parts; an interface and a physical part...
            </p>
            
            <br>
            <p>Without any coding the toolkit lets you:</p>
            <ul>
            <li>Add friends to be aware of</li>
            <li>Decide what location- information to share with friends</li>
            <li>Decide what location- information to receive from friends </li>
            <li>Decide how this location- information is presented</li>
            <li>Physically plug on the chosen parts to the aWearable</li>
            </ul>
            <p><i>(See the <a href="how_to.html">'How-To'</a> for more details on these steps)</i></p>
            </div>
            
